  "detailed_description": "A platforming adventure game with a new take on combos, dare you adventure into the world of Filly Astray and face the monsters and mayhem within?!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602780/extras/2e535d5fd96e3565134d933631615714.poster.avif?t=1698917188\" width=724 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602780/extras/2e535d5fd96e3565134d933631615714.webm?t=1698917188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602780/extras/2e535d5fd96e3565134d933631615714.mp4?t=1698917188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Chain attacks for increasing damage, but tread carefully – a single miss and you'll be sent tumbling. Inspired by the weight and feel of fighting games, Filly astray aims to bring some of that satisfaction to single player action.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602780/extras/0cc3b1f587299a9c1fda5d56dafe8074.apng?t=1698917188\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602780/extras/0cc3b1f587299a9c1fda5d56dafe8074.poster.avif?t=1698917188\" class=\"bb_img\" width=614 height=128 /></picture></span><br><br>Travel through 6ish different enviroments fighting your way through a varied cast of enemies. Filly Astray contrains 2-5 hours of content for a first play through, as well as challenges to make it interesting for multiple playthroughs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602780/extras/7255dcc638a043501bf05c139c234fc1.poster.avif?t=1698917188\" width=614 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602780/extras/7255dcc638a043501bf05c139c234fc1.webm?t=1698917188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Test your mettle against 5 bosses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602780/extras/52397200295a9718ecbfe18fb3093b17.avif?t=1698917188\" width=128 height=128 /></span><br><br>Be a cute filly.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602780/extras/eb2f64f6873b483fc499c652ef0aae41.avif?t=1698917188\" width=614 height=379 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "A platforming adventure game with a new take on combos, dare you adventure into the world of Filly Astray and face the monsters and mayhem within?!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602780/extras/2e535d5fd96e3565134d933631615714.poster.avif?t=1698917188\" width=724 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602780/extras/2e535d5fd96e3565134d933631615714.webm?t=1698917188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602780/extras/2e535d5fd96e3565134d933631615714.mp4?t=1698917188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Chain attacks for increasing damage, but tread carefully – a single miss and you'll be sent tumbling. Inspired by the weight and feel of fighting games, Filly astray aims to bring some of that satisfaction to single player action.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602780/extras/0cc3b1f587299a9c1fda5d56dafe8074.apng?t=1698917188\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602780/extras/0cc3b1f587299a9c1fda5d56dafe8074.poster.avif?t=1698917188\" class=\"bb_img\" width=614 height=128 /></picture></span><br><br>Travel through 6ish different enviroments fighting your way through a varied cast of enemies. Filly Astray contrains 2-5 hours of content for a first play through, as well as challenges to make it interesting for multiple playthroughs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602780/extras/7255dcc638a043501bf05c139c234fc1.poster.avif?t=1698917188\" width=614 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602780/extras/7255dcc638a043501bf05c139c234fc1.webm?t=1698917188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Test your mettle against 5 bosses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602780/extras/52397200295a9718ecbfe18fb3093b17.avif?t=1698917188\" width=128 height=128 /></span><br><br>Be a cute filly.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602780/extras/eb2f64f6873b483fc499c652ef0aae41.avif?t=1698917188\" width=614 height=379 /></span>",
